# GitHub Linguist overrides — keep the Languages bar representative of the
# R package, not its rendered documentation.
#
# Rendered vignette / Quarto article HTML (e.g. the ~1.9 MB
# vignettes/articles/example-ae.html) are build artifacts, not source code.
# Mark all HTML — plus the supporting CSS/JS that ships with the docs — as
# documentation so they are excluded from the language statistics while
# remaining browsable in the repo.
*.html linguist-documentation
*.css  linguist-documentation
*.js   linguist-documentation

# Example RTF deliverables under inst/rtf-examples/ are rendered package
# OUTPUT shown in the documentation, not source code. Keep them, but exclude
# them from the Languages bar.
*.rtf  linguist-documentation
